Description:
You arrive at a strange island marked by a large monkey head sculpted into the rock, forming a cavern.

Inside, a ghostly monkey materializes before you and demands a blood sacrifice in exchange for great wisdom.

The monkey laughs as the cavern entrance seals shut, proclaiming that it will only reopen once blood has been spilled.
DescriptionAction: A ghostly blade materializes before you. Who will wield it?
